{"tid":1545062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理性處理831消息","createTime":"2019-09-05T18:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T11:32:01.000Z","uid":313312,"like":55,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"76781014ae112660ed75a188776b1fafa9f95bc3","tid":1545062,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T18:55:39.000Z","msg":"依家開始有好多小道消息，而好多都無實質證明。<br />\n<br />\n我地面對依種消息態度，先唔抗拒冇實質證據，當佢係一個謠言，一個陰謀論，分析當中論點，同組織各種說法，睇下可唔可以組織成個事件。<br />\n<br />\n去到依刻真相好難浮現，只有謠言先可以迫出真相，謠言越多人討論，壓力越大，政府要辟謠非常之簡單就係交出cctv，一個咁簡單動作可以解除大家疑慮，都唔做只會瓜田李下。<br />\n<br />\n呼籲大家唔好做標題黨，唔很定，唔好講到實牙實齒，大家以一個謠言去討論，就唔洗驚抄車。<br />\n<br />\n而且係依件事上，真假有人死，只要政府交出cctv都對我地有利，可以成為鐵證831沒差別黑警恐襲<br />\n<br />\n要求交出831太子cctv，釋除疑慮"},{"pid":"271db68d8a6faf5ce276433ff79746ba52e93a0e","tid":1545062,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T18:55:48.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"823ba303d7902485109ac1783c4f0ec68199202a","tid":1545062,"uid":313312,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"271db68d8a6faf5ce276433ff79746ba52e93a0e","tid":1545062,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T18:55:48.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s